==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Designment
<hw>De*sign"ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Delineation; sketch; design; ideal; invention.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>For though that some mean artist's skill were shown⟦br⟧
In mingling colors, or in placing light,⟦br⟧
Yet still the fair <qex>designment</qex> was his own.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Design; purpose; scheme.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Desilver</ent>⟦br⟧
